{"tid":1637334,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱個frd話去食M記，俾我屌到跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:42:40.000Z","uid":150100,"like":14,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"563e6f08b8a491ca171183ad65e11a7cc157939d","tid":1637334,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我地一班大學friend就成日出街食飯嘅，唔係自助餐就放題，唔係放題就食西餐据牛排燒羊架，平均一餐2、300蚊走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁講真，真係一啲都唔過份囉，話曬我地都係大學生，天之驕子嚟㗎嘛，唔通食啲100蚊都唔駛嘅垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏我地其中一個friend就成撚日呻窮，今日佢竟然話不如食M記算啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：窮撚friend<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母，竟然叫我地成班大學生食豬餿，上次買咗個M記外賣返歸餵狗，連我屋企隻狗都唔撚食呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但係我冇錢&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢唔識問老母攞？你啞定弱智？<br />\n<br />\n屌屌下我實在忍唔撚住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 你同我跪喺度！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友又真係一嘢跪咗喺度，仲開始流埋馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我冇老豆老母㗎，屋企攞綜援㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢就咪學人埋堆啦，躪返屋企食狗屎啦<br />\n<br />\n之後我就同班friend由得佢跪喺度走咗去食好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好嘢！"},{"pid":"0e4eadf74fa934daf03ac63d85266bd7ab569f6c","tid":1637334,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"請文宣<br />\n<br />\n1. 即時叫停裝修、加強宣揚黑警恐怖分子施襲平民<br />\n2. 設立停火期（等林鄭知邊個先係打骰）<br />\n3. 答應五大訴求、否則後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c91c1ea46ae6213bfa10f3346ca7327f1b39e3","tid":1637334,"uid":204943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"樓主已經無晒貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57cf44bb86514a85b8763eb621dbf30e33321bb","tid":1637334,"uid":145449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"又跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a52298064c3ca9e543a5b91f0a220c093d54fb","tid":1637334,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"Harden 你同我跪喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49910fb789ccba7f5effa33ac0470f1c00d3bce7","tid":1637334,"uid":244303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"喂，我撐你喎樓豬<br />\n窮人學乜尻人埋堆？跳樓死啦屌<br />\n<br />\n利申：樓豬死未"},{"pid":"fa8a976713664c0e753e357fd93832653a8b8a10","tid":1637334,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a52298064c3ca9e543a5b91f0a220c093d54fb","tid":1637334,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"Harden 你同我跪喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/